dupiR is an R package for Bayesian inference using discrete uniform priors. It has been developed by Federico Comoglio (ETH Zurich) and Maurizio Rinaldi (University of Piemonte Orientale).

This GitHub repository contains a first release of the package and will accommodate subsequent updates.

Feel free to contact us at:
